### 1. Barcha narx paketlarini ko'rish
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/tiers
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Har bir slide narxini ko'rish
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/per-slide
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. 5 ta slide uchun narxni hisoblash
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/calculate?num_slides=5
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. 10 ta slide uchun narxni hisoblash
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/calculate?num_slides=10
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. 25 ta slide uchun narxni hisoblash
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/calculate?num_slides=25
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. POST so'rovi bilan narxni hisoblash
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/pricing/estimate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "num_slides": 15
}

###

### 7. Root endpoint
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Accept: application/json